New SVG based metatheme for GNOME 2.2. This one is
based upon the beautiful Nuvola icons by David Vignoni. 
It includes a special Nuvola GTK+ by Andrew Johnson using his theme
engine, smooth.
Also included is a Nuvola version of the GnomeIridium metacity theme,
the Nuvola version done by Josselin Mouette.
